item.title: Memes on copy pasting code from Stackoverflow
item.description: We have all copied code from stackoverflow.com, github.com and from other sources. Please mention other sources to copy code from. These websites has helped us a lot to become a good programmer. Stackoverflow was launched on 2008 by Jeff Atwood and Joel Spolsky. It is written in C#. It is owned by Stack Exchange Network. Stack Exchange Network has some good websites too. codereview.stackexchange has helped me a lot as a programmer.
